285
00:34:09,123 --> 00:34:12,956
<i>Dlatego w pełni oddaję...</i>

286
00:34:13,040 --> 00:34:14,040
Dość tego!

287
00:34:14,123 --> 00:34:16,498
<i>...ciało swe</i>

288
00:34:16,581 --> 00:34:19,206
<i>I duszę</i>

289
